  <LINE>GLASGOW CAITHNESS-SHIRE FRIENDLY.</LINE>
  <LINE>Instituted 1837.</LINE>
  <LINE>The principal objects of this Society, the qualifi-</LINE>
  <LINE>cation for membership of which consists in a small</LINE>
  <LINE>annual payment, are to maintain a friendly inter-</LINE>
  <LINE>course amongst Caithness men residing in Glasgow,</LINE>
  <LINE>and to afford temporary relief to such of their coun-</LINE>
  <LINE>trymen as may be in want.</LINE>
